{"tid":2194534,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla嘅極限已經到左 輪到我嘅Nikola發揮喇","createTime":"2020-09-08T14:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:07:25.000Z","uid":108201,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"007ede1210fbe9fe8802365e4d59534375c2d44a","tid":2194534,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"電動卡車公司Nikola與通用汽車組成戰略合作<br />\n8/9/2020 21:19&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nNikola宣布, 將會與通用汽車合作生產電動皮卡車「Badger」, 產品將會使用通用汽的Ultium電池技術, 通用汽車將會取得Nikola一成一股權, 約值20億美元的股份.<br />\n<br />\nNikola創辦人兼執行主席米爾頓在聲明中表示, 公司是全球其中一間最創新的企業, 而通用汽是其中一間最好的工程及製造企業, 雙方的合作是夢寐以求.<br />\n<br />\n公司預計在十二月初發表電動皮卡車「Badger」詳情, 2022年開始生產.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20200908211922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200908211922&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f7eac9f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20200908211922</a>"},{"pid":"c97fde7528f610a216d3318b8453d802f63f3b78","tid":2194534,"uid":42751,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"皮卡車同比卡超有關？"},{"pid":"5b71975332322aa840085fb9d6b31c0fc8dc1c01","tid":2194534,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"Nikola NKLA 依家升緊40％<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad9cbb86057b2916f73f00ed095ea2c33fd3884","tid":2194534,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c97fde7528f610a216d3318b8453d802f63f3b78","tid":2194534,"uid":42751,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"皮卡車同比卡超有關？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"你可以理解為貨櫃車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3a7bad2d86a49ee3f9a24f4e24